sequenceDiagram
  participant Task as COMP-DEVICE-001 StartupTask
  participant Camera as MediaCapture camera
  participant Detector as COMP-DEVICE-002 LocalFaceDetector
  participant Persister as COMP-DEVICE-003 AzureImagePersister
  participant Blob as Blob Storage
  participant IoTHub as IoT Hub

  Task->>Task: Initialize DI and FaceDetector if supported
  Task->>Camera: FindAllAsync video capture devices
  Task->>Camera: InitializeAsync and SetMaxResolution
  loop while true, each camera
    Task->>Camera: CapturePhotoToStreamAsync JPEG
    Camera-->>Task: BitmapDecoder and cloned stream
    Task-)Detector: ProcessImageAsync not awaited
    Detector->>Detector: Convert to Gray8 SoftwareBitmap
    Detector->>Detector: DetectFacesAsync
    loop each detected face
      Detector->>Detector: Enlarge face box, crop, encode JPEG
      Detector->>Persister: PersistAsync(face stream, cameraId)
      Persister->>Blob: Upload {deviceId}/{guid}.jpg
      Blob-->>Persister: Upload complete
      Persister->>IoTHub: SendEventAsync {deviceId, blobName, cameraId}
      IoTHub-->>Persister: Send complete
    end
  end
  Note over Task,Persister: No cancellation/backpressure observed; exceptions in detector are swallowed after Debug logging
